#strong[What stories do people tell about the past that are wrong?]


#hint["Everyone knows" the old king was a hero, or that the elves started the war, or that the magic died on its own. But what if the accepted version is incomplete, distorted, or an outright lie? Wrong history believed as fact is one of the richest sources of conflict in storytelling.]


#writing-box(
  label: "Your Answer",
